sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / CLI / SDK
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Queue as BullMQ Agent Queue
    participant Worker as Agent Worker
    participant Browser as Playwright Browser
    participant LLM as LLM Provider
    participant Store as Postgres / Redis

    User->>API: POST /v1/agent/run { goal, url }
    API->>Queue: Enqueue agent job
    API-->>User: { runId, status: "queued" }

    User->>API: GET /v1/agent/run/{runId}
    API-->>User: { status: "queued" }

    Queue->>Worker: Dequeue job
    Worker->>Store: Create run record
    Worker->>API: Update status to "running"
    API-->>User: (via poll) { status: "running" }

    loop Each Step (max 20)
        Worker->>Browser: Navigate / screenshot
        Browser-->>Worker: Page state
        Worker->>LLM: Analyze + plan next action
        LLM-->>Worker: { thought, action }
        Worker->>Store: Save agent event
        User->>API: GET /v1/agent/run/{runId}/events
        API-->>User: SSE stream of events
    end

    Worker->>Store: Save final result
    Worker->>API: Update status to "succeeded"
    API-->>User: (via poll) { status: "succeeded" }

    User->>API: GET /v1/agent/run/{runId}/result
    API-->>User: { result, steps, trace }
